{"tid":1005942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"用違反自然定律呢個原因去反LGBT係好戇鳩","createTime":"2019-02-02T14:42:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T06:21:13.000Z","uid":48234,"like":75,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"368ca1b02a46adf8a3f3b3fc462f3bb58ee34445","tid":1005942,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"先分開LGB同T<br />\nL同G分別係女性，男性同性戀<br />\nWikipedia: 動物同性性行為<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%25A1%258C%25E7%2582%25BA&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=6c961439\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%80%A7%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA</a><br />\n求其一個source已經推翻L同G違反自然<br />\nB,同上述兩者類似,所以都可以推翻埋<br />\n<br />\n呢次講T<br />\n動物變性<br />\nBroadly: Yes, There are trans animals (英文注意)<br />\n<a href=\"https://broadly.vice.com/en_us/article/8x8bez/yes-there-are-trans-animals\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbroadly.vice.com%2Fen_us%2Farticle%2F8x8bez%2Fyes-there-are-trans-animals&d=iQRxYBMNZOojMWQldZVC2Rdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=cdb90659\" target=\"_blank\">https://broadly.vice.com/en_us/article/8x8bez/yes-there-are-trans-animals</a><br />\n哦，動物可以變性適應環境，人類變性就要屌?<br />\n人類變性都係為咗適應自己心理，周圍環境咋喎<br />\n<br />\n再講，人類都係自然產生出嚟，人類嘅複雜思想、進化都係自然演變<br />\n一層又一層嘅自然演變，突然間就會有人屌乜撚嘢違反自然定律<br />\n根本呢句話講嚟都戇鳩<br />\n如果你要自然，點解而家又咁撚多科技?<br />\n你硬要講，剩係你上連登用嘅電腦，手提電話，都係非自然啦<br />\n咁人哋LGBT影響唔撚到你，同你唔撚識，又關你撚事?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">如果你要用違反自然定律嚟屌LGBT,唔該咪撚上連登<br />\n因為剩係上連登個行為本身就係違反自然定律</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9ddcd9cce330135d9f5d238d9d6290b6bf0d3a4","tid":1005942,"uid":20241,"like":20,"dislike":37,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:44:15.000Z","msg":"試但啦總知就係變態<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9d301e97cf031f0b15592d1e1228eb930f2798f","tid":1005942,"uid":161195,"like":25,"dislike":25,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e2791cb92cc48958fe9dee0d4d3e5c2fbb3030d","tid":1005942,"uid":49392,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:51:47.000Z","msg":"成日有新聞爆出反同人士其實係基，連登咁多反基人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b98343d4238e720ae6caa32bf5faf2b611cf57","tid":1005942,"uid":161195,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:52:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"360c8814b4e9f10f3dd0a5b4a3c6ff9ccd2e76bf","tid":1005942,"uid":161195,"like":10,"dislike":11,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:53:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b0fde965775543f01aaf760d184776c30e7db2d","tid":1005942,"uid":4973,"like":13,"dislike":10,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:54:03.000Z","msg":"動物係因應繁殖先變性<br />\n人類變性等同捨棄繁殖呢個選擇<br />\n點可以擺埋嚟講? <br />\n雖然歧視人係唔啱,但係LGBT 係社會上嘅異類, 俾人歧視係正常㗎喎"},{"pid":"0fdbfb75bb6d9a5bc9a993a516179d3909bcaf4c","tid":1005942,"uid":52942,"like":24,"dislike":12,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"反LGBT根本唔使原因"},{"pid":"992c9c8804fb0d8a5ef0e82debb965ec5ad8d32e","tid":1005942,"uid":163350,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:55:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f45d31f304ab54ca3c4badc903760f43f7505d02","tid":1005942,"uid":163350,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b24229cbd09a5d2d6940a22b24195394cdb717f","tid":1005942,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:56:18.000Z","msg":"Op想籌錢變性<br />\n大家體諒下"},{"pid":"169f379c3c772af0d3f605c05a26375d1c056ce7","tid":1005942,"uid":78429,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T14:57:45.000Z",